parameters.description:
An integer that represents what is being included.
 
            It works as a bitmask and uses the following values for each annotation types:
 
            PositiveControlFlag = 1;
 
            RejectedFlag = 2;
 
            OriginalFlag = 4;
 
            ConfirmationFlag = 8;
 
            DeletedFlag = 16;
 
            AnimalControlFlag = 32;
 
            SecondConfirmationFlag = 64;
 
            VerificationFlag = 128;
 
            NoAnnotationFlag = 256;

 
            To include multiple annotation ids, you add their sum as a single number.

  
            For example, if you want to include annotations with ids 1, 32 and 8, you call annotation=41

